data.description: Welcome home to this charming abode located in the tranquil neighborhood of Atascocita Trace in Humble, Texas. This well-maintained residence offers three bedrooms and two baths, providing comfortable living space for its occupants. The interior features a spacious layout with an open-concept design that creates a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and the primary bath has a separate garden tub and a walk-in shower. Utility room is located inside of home with the Washer & Dryer included with purchase. Come enjoy easy access to Beltway 8 , I-69/ HWY 59, FM-1960 RD, shopping, dining, parks, IAH airport, and recreational facilities. With its comfortable living spaces and a location that offers the best of suburban living, 2510 Benelli Court is a desirable home for those seeking a harmonious blend of comfort and convenience.  Schedule a showing today.
